 And the following HTML at the bottom of each "page" to add the page break: <div class="page-break"></div> If I click the reports tab and use the Adobe PDF printer, I'm able to generate a pdf that is pretty close to what I need for paper copies except that it does not contain the page breaks!!!  And if I try to print it out it also does not contain the page breaks. Thank you, Andrew J. Leer
